<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/boundary-commission-for-wales> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Boundary Commission for Wales (BCW) carries out boundary reviews of parliamentary constituencies in Wales, and submits its recommendations to the government. BCW is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ."@en .
